I"Z<h4 id="exercise-0-dot-gif">Exercise 0: dot gif</h4>

<p>A simple way to start thinking about motion is through a gif, a short animated image that is controlled through individual frames. The gif should tell a (very short) story that is unique to you. Make a 15 to 30 frame, greater than 1 second, looping gif that tells that story.</p>

<h5 id="technical-requirements">Technical Requirements</h5>

<ul>
  <li>15 to 30 frames (or more)</li>
  <li>at least 1 second of animation</li>
  <li>infinite loop</li>
  <li>gif format</li>
</ul>

